<abstract><t>This memo describes a new RFC 2822 message header, &quot;Message-Context&quot;. This header provides information about the context and presentation characteristics of a message. A receiving user agent (UA) may use this information as a hint to optimally present the message.  [STANDARDS-TRACK]</t></abstract>
